article_title: What's In A Name? Preventing A Dangerous Race To The Bottom In Biotechnology

article_metadata.author: Tomas Philipson

og.description: As the debate over whether to ban differential naming of biosimilars continues, the implications for both quality and price competition need to be considered more carefully.
